well as the actual violence that people in poorer communities across the US=
 experience. The short version is simple =E2=80=94 it may be more stimulati=
ng, and glamorous if the violence is upped a couple of clicks. But then you=
 usually don=E2=80=99t survive it. You get killed, or you kill someone and =
